those fighting the regime. You should know that you are sons of 
Rwanda. The Republican Democratic Movement [MDR] cannot accept 
people using their grief as a pretext to kill indiscriminately 
and for this to be accepted by senior officers. We cannot just 
stand by and watch. The MDR and other parties that favor change 
