<H4>    RPF Rejects Continued French Presence </H4>

<F P=102> EA1204161994 (Clandestine) Radio Muhabura in Kinyarwanda to 
Rwanda 1015 GMT 12 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> EA1204161994 </F>
