<DOCNO> FBIS4-685 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drafr072_c_94015" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-AFR-94-072 </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  13 Apr 1994 </DATE1>

