<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Statement issued by the Independent Electoral Commission on </F>
13 April on the SAPA PR Wire Service] 
  [Text] A total of 77 international organisations and 26 
local organisations have been accredited by the monitoring 
directorate, according to Lucia Mtshali of the Department of 
Accreditation and Logistics at national office. This does not 
include the inter-governmental organisations like the United 
Nations, the OAU and the European Community. 
  The deadline for the accredition of international and local 
organisations for the purpose of observing the elections, 
expired on March 27. A few late applications have been accepted. 


