<H3> <TI>   Van der Walt: Fair Election Possible </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Van der Walt: Fair Election Possible </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   MB1504095894 Johannesburg SABC TV 1 Network in English 0500 
