  [Text] Bophuthatsawana co-adminstartor Tjaart van der Walt 
has denied reports that the situation in the former homeland is 
getting out of control. 
  Dr. van der Walt said that while he and his 
co-administrator, 
Mr. Job Makgoro, had held heated talks with Bophuthatswana 
police on pension payouts, he believed that the police were 
still committed to maintaining law and order. He said that he 
and Bophuthatswana and South African Police officials were 
unanimous in feeling that while the situation was volatile, it 
